{"tid":1215821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎睇下香港暴徒做咗乜","createTime":"2019-06-13T08:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T08:44:20.000Z","uid":216523,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0ad1d3c79b128df7fc015e96af8f7712e34057e3","tid":1215821,"uid":216523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:20:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LUxq7VC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLUxq7VC.gif&h=721ac9a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名少年於金鐘一帶背向警察站立，遭十多名速龍小隊成員<span style=\"color: red;\">強行拉扯到地上用警棍圍毆</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aQu85Ja.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaQu85Ja.gif&h=0ec58946&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名少女下午於立法會地下門外落單，遭近十名警員<span style=\"color: red;\">以盾牌及警棍按倒地上瘋狂圍毆</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wk41Gxi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwk41Gxi.gif&h=5c8616cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名手無寸鐵市民於大會堂對出方向，遭4-5名警員<span style=\"color: red;\">揮棍不停攻擊頭部倒地。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/4g17BRj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4g17BRj.gif&h=509faf8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名外藉男子於愛丁堡廣場附近，因行動不便獨自坐於花槽旁，<span style=\"color: red;\">遭警員以胡椒噴劑近距離向臉部射擊。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eLz5ovx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeLz5ovx.gif&h=58851dc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i8PQzCe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi8PQzCe.gif&h=58a9a71f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UvSnqJW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUvSnqJW.gif&h=c1469b1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>下午時份於金鐘天橋附近一帶，一名中年婦人向警員哭求停止對香港人使用武力，<span style=\"color: red;\">遭警員近距離以不明武器擊中頭部。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/d6KQzNf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd6KQzNf.gif&h=b3ebd9eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名市民於金鐘橋底下，遭警員<span style=\"color: red;\">以布袋彈瞄準頭部射擊</span>。</strong>"},{"pid":"82e1fa64c8b4fdddd0504e365fb17b63acf6fd2c","tid":1215821,"uid":216523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:24:20.000Z","msg":"推到所有香港人睇到班暴徒做咗啲乜"},{"pid":"279dd36386632290cb9713b1953dfd30e18f3a92","tid":1215821,"uid":216523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:26:14.000Z","msg":"強烈譴責暴徒暴力行為"},{"pid":"f51468b90c569c8f51d7ad4cb508ac58d1aa0e89","tid":1215821,"uid":216523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:28:22.000Z","msg":"暴徒唔死都冇撚用 嚴重破壞香港秩序"},{"pid":"3a51159486c2ab14e4e494330a70a83351dad0e2","tid":1215821,"uid":216523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:30:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"336e6f427ed59bc5be6b62ea1955391d230a4653","tid":1215821,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:30:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5dbc4eec9d4a8eaebb2aa0b058012050cdd33507","tid":1215821,"uid":216523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:33:23.000Z","msg":"暴徒應得到應有嘅懲罰"},{"pid":"96d9897f6e71ff8b69f8fc6ec4796e1d6231688c","tid":1215821,"uid":119347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:44:20.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}